name: NFCORE_RNASEQ:RNASEQ:PREPARE_GENOME:UNTAR_SALMON_INDEX (salmon.tar.gz)

## If just files or multiple directories, place all in prefix

    tar \
        -C salmon --strip-components 1 \
        -xavf \
         \
        salmon.tar.gz \
        --no-same-owner

        -C salmon \
        -xavf \
         \
        salmon.tar.gz \

fi
